      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im working on this script for a dark comedy/satire and im trying to be really careful about not accidentally falling into lazy tropes. can you give me a list of like, 5 or 6 of the most common racial stereotypes used in hollywood movies? i just want to make sure i know what they are so i can avoid them or maybe subvert them in the writing.",
